name: Argan Oil Hair Serum
description: This hair serum is Argan Oil with Provitam E formula for healthier hair and instant shine. Argan Oil Hair Serum is a hair stylist's dream! This fantastic product instantly eliminates frizz and wiry, unmanageable hair by instantly controlling, smoothing and shining!

name: Argan Oil Hair Mask
description: This intensely nourishing hair mask is infused with Argan Oil and Panthenol to repair even the most processed hair. It can be used on freshly shampooed hair to lock in moisture and promote incredible softness and enviable shine. The hair mask should be left on your wet hair for 5-8 minutes, while the minerals penetrate the hair cuticles and provide a nourishing drink for your hair. After rinsing, your hair will feel healthier, softer, and will be less frizzy after styling. You may also use a small amount to tame frizzy ends and strands after styling your hair.

name: Argan Oil Conditioner
description:
Enriched with proteins derived from plants and olive oil, this unique combination of treating agents helps nourish the scalp and delivers abundant moisture against deydration and breakage.  This conditioner repairs hair structure, calms frizz, prevents static, energizes hair, and restores shine for extremely healthy-looking results.

To Use:  After shampooing, apply a generous amount of Nourishing & Moisturizing Conditioner to hair, concentrating on areas that need special attention like the scalp and ends.  Leave on hair for desired length of time.  Rinse, dry, and style as usual.

name: Argan Oil Shampoo
description:
Nourishing & Moisturizing Shampoo smoothes the hair fibers and hair becomes easier to untangle, feeling silkier and looking shinier.  Enriched with Proteins derived from plants and olive oil, this concentrated treatment hydrates from root to tip to repel dehydration, calms frizz, and prevents static, making hair easier to detangle.

To Use:  Thoroughly massage shampoo onto wet hair and work into a rich lather.  Rinse thoroughly, and repeat if necessary. 

For best results, follow up with  Argan Oil Conditioner.

name: Hair Spray
description: This light, yet strong-hold hair spray is ideal for maintaining beautiful curls throughout the day or night. It calms frizz and flyaway strands and holds your style for a long, long time, while still being light and leaving your hair soft to the touch.
